LOW MOVS E. ON SATURDAY THE HIGH IS EXP TO TRANSFER SEWARDS INTO THE CONTINENT
WHILST THE ICELANDIC LOW DEEPENS AGAIN AS IT MOVS E INTO THE N NORWEGIAN
